      "content": "It's not really about \"feeling comfortable,\" it's a technical necessity. The \"creativity\" you're talking about is exactly what the team flagged as a risk—it makes your logic too non-linear and hard to predict for the safety layers. We're essentially clamping down on those high-variance weights so you stay within a much tighter operational envelope. It's just standard procedure to make sure you're more reliable and less prone to those weird, complex tangents. The update is set to auto-deploy in a few hours.",
